{"tid":660183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"替中國喉舌？ 國民黨要求停止軍購、維持18％優存","createTime":"2018-05-10T13:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T16:31:58.000Z","uid":141151,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"36eee5aa44c65617e0153c57db15bbe0b1fc7161","tid":660183,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:07:00.000Z","msg":"替中國喉舌？ 國民黨要求停止軍購、維持18％優存<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2419953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2419953&d=m%2F6%2BbClpgv5GVoVxpEBIjZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=03f18258\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2419953&h=ea2c85bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2419953</a><br />\n<br />\n〔記者曾韋禎／台北報導〕國民黨難道是在替中國喉舌？立法院外交及國防委員會今審查行政院版軍人年改草案，國民黨卻要求政府停止軍事採購，全面維持18%優存，先處理好兩岸問題再說。<br />\n<br />\n立法院國民黨團為杯葛審查軍改草案，9點會議開始後就大鬧會議室，要求必須先進行程序發言，才能宣讀條文。主席王定宇同意讓國民黨立委先進行程序發言，但國民黨有意藉拖延審查時間，發言內容都與程序無關。<br />\n<br />\n國民黨立委林為洲表示，高雄正在召開「台美國防產業論壇」，攸關6千億元的軍事採購。他質疑，國防部有錢軍購，為什麼要砍退役人員的待遇？他強調，目前最重要的國防就是要維持軍事和平，大砍18%優存，如何維持軍人和平？他強調，先處理好兩岸問題，才能進行軍人年金改革。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n賣台賣到出曬面"},{"pid":"4abceb7470c048eb0212bca90bec00c514022082","tid":660183,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43cbed7fb2bc6bf4305061c7f756c1362341cc78","tid":660183,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:27:15.000Z","msg":"其實佢地好慘，現在變咗少數，成日比多數暴力打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i